  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbf \u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd ; \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Girl abduction case in Jaffna; Two arrested",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two youths have been arrested and police are investigating a complaint lodged at the police station by relatives that a girl had been abducted in Jaffna.",
        "A complaint was lodged at the Jaffna Police Station by relatives that a girl from the vicinity of Jaffna was abducted last Friday in Jaffna.",
        "The girl was rescued by the Kilinochchi Police from the Kilinochchi area on Monday and admitted to the Kilinochchi Base Road.",
        "Meanwhile, the girl's relatives had complained to the Northern Province Governor's Office that the Jaffna police had not carried out a proper investigation into their complaint and that the police had not taken any action to inform the police that they had been subjected to a series of threats by a group of youths living in their area.",
        "Following this, the Jaffna Police have arrested two youths on suspicion and detained them at the Jaffna Police Station based on the confession of the girl's relatives."
      ],
